srl.wordlist
Class WordList

java.lang.Object
  srl.wordlist.WordList

public class WordList
extends java.lang.Object

A set of word lists. The individual values are stored in as WordList.Entry objects. All wordlists are indexed globally and may be accessed through functions on this list (this is so that a wordlist may be found by its identifier alone without knowing its set)
